REMOVAL METHOD¶

  1. OUTLIER REMOVAL USING IQR (WAS LATER DISCRADED AS THE PERCENTILE METHOD WAS MUCH MORE EFFECIENT)

q1=df.Age.quantile(0.25) print(q1) q3=df.Age.quantile(0.75) print(q3)

IQR=q3-q1 IQR

upper_limit=q3+1.5*IQR upper_limit

lower_limit=q1-1.5*IQR lower_limit

df=df[df.Age<upper_limit]

df.shape

df=df[df.Age>lower_limit]

df.shape
